  <div class="page">
    <p>The encryption &amp; secret must capture the permissions  We use Wildcard Identity Based Encryption (WIBE) [Abdalla, 2006]  Every entity has a WIBE master key</p>
    <p>No PKG, every entity has their own system  Used just for RDE, nothing else</p>
    <p>When you create attestation (grant permissions)  Form WIBE ID = F(permissions)  Generate private key for that ID using granting entity master key  Include in attestation  Encrypt attestation using WIBE params for recipient using same ID</p>
    <p>This is simplified, please see paper for more details</p>
